				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Mages are by far the MOST powerful character in the game, so thus it is only proper that we have the hardest quest in the game also, most of the quest and it's items you can do up to level 50, at 50 I would recommend the quest for your epic, seeing as at that point you are doing Plane Raids anyways, you can get your items with your raiding members no problem, the Magi'Kot pages you can obtain at level 40 no problem, the torn pages of mastery from 25-30, all the items Jennus needs at level 40-49,items for Tiblner and Jinalis at 50 with a partner, and the items for Kihun at level 50-51...The hardest part of your epic is getting the Pegasus Feathered Cloak off Quillmane, believe it or not, everything else is easy enough to kill with a partner, and the Plane items with your raiding group...after you have finished Kihun's quest, and make sure you have completed EVERYTHING up until then, the MASTER OF THE ELEMENTS, spawns, you MUST give him all the Elements of Fire, Water,Earth and Air, then you will get your scroll ....good luck all and remember, that you ARE the most powerful character in the game and that our quest HAS to be this hard...in order for Balance<BR>
